                                    </item>
                                </list>
                            </additions>
                        </physDesc>
                        <history>
                            <origin>Since the copier is mentioned by the same name <persName ref="PRS15382WaldaIya">Walda ʾIyasus</persName>. The same
                                name appears as copier for <ref target="#p2"/>. It is therefore likely, that both codicological units have been produced 
                                by the same copier around the same time, i.e.
                                <origDate notBefore="1875" notAfter="1925">the end of the nineteenth or beginning of the twentieth century</origDate>.
                            </origin>
                        </history>
